    <h3>Tooltips</h3>
    <p>You can display tooltips on various elements by adding a <code>rel="tooltip"</code> and <code>title</code> attribute to any element.  Here we use buttons as examples.  You can also optionally specify direction by adding a <code>data-placement</code> attribute.</p>
    <div class="btn-toolbar">
